parameters: Kru: "I'm home."
Maid: "Welcome back."
Kru: "I'm always causing you trouble, aren't I?"
Maid: "No, no. I receive a generous salary, so..."

Kru: "No, it's only natural since I leave everything concerning my personal
affairs to you."

Maid: "If left alone, Kru-san would spend days in a daze without eating
anything. That's not good, you need to eat properly since you're young."
Kru: "Yes."
Maid: "And you should also find yourself a wife."
Kru: "Ugh..."
Maid: "...As usual, you avoid that kind of talk, huh?"
Kru: "...I'm sorry."

Maid: "I'm just worried about you... Kru-san. Life is a bit too long to
live it alone."
Kru: "...Yes."

Maid: "However, when living with someone else, time flies by in the blink
of an eye... It's quite cruel, isn't it?"
Kru: "...Yes."
Maid: "Well then, there's a good marriage proposal for you!"
Kru: "...Please spare me."
Maid: "Hahaha! I thought you'd say that and turned it down already."
Kru: "Hahaha! As expected of you."

Maid: "Well then, I'll be leaving. The meal is freshly made, so please eat
it soon."
Kru: "Thank you very much. Good work today."
This is my current life...

I have a fulfilling job, the means to employ a maid, a home, and each day
passes by peacefully.

The daily growth of the children teaches me that yesterday and today are
different, but other than that, my days are unchanging.
I have a daily routine as well...
ガブ

In the time before bed. Quietly, I reminisce about the days spent with
Umi...

As the hustle and bustle of the town fades, the sound of the waves gently
emerges, luring my consciousness to the past.
What I remember are mostly mundane, ordinary memories.
Touching upon those memories until sleepiness arrives, I gaze outside.
That was my only pleasure.
Days passed by in such a manner...
